descriptionHtml:
This is the first mod I've uploaded to nexus.  I've made several mods in the past.  This is a small player home mod.
You will find it north of Anga's Mill.  You'll find a bunch of stairs, once you've gone up the stairs you'll find a cave entrance.  Go through it and there you
are, your new home.  There is nothing special about the house except for a sword that I made a personal enchantment for.  You'll find a forge behind the house and a chest full of supplies.  If you find any bugs, or anything that shouldn't be there, please leave a comment.  You'll find a deed on the table in front of the fire place.  The only issue is I couldn't fix the entrance so you may not be able to get in without using the "tcl" cheat.
author: ilawana
